	   <tr><td colspan=2>It seems that lately on the Cazic-Thule server, the BM has a habit of becoming a giants pet when she wanders to close to the regular frost giant scouts.&nbsp;&nbsp;This is a Bug in the quest that has not been fixed yet.  There is an easy way to fix this bug, which led to me getting my legs tonight...<br><br>1.  Keep your normal group up near Fergul, but have one person set aside for giant clearing.<br><br>2.  Announce to the zone that you are training giants to the EW zone, and start pulling every giant you see to EW.<br><br>One of my guildies did this tonight, dragging 12 giants to zone, and the BM had no problems, no Bugs.  Just don't stop running...they will keep up.<br><br>Tadayna Wolfsong<br>Master of Everything<br>Nearly Grandmaster in Tailoring<br>Cazic-Thule Server<br>Officer for Avatars of Shadows<br>2nd try on Kromriff Leggings<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
